Ann Gillis https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Ann_Gillis 0 Alma Mabel (Ann) Conner (February 12, 1927 – January 31, 2018), known professionally as Ann Gillis, was an American actress, best known for her film roles as a child actress. She was sometimes credited as Anne Gillis or Ann Gilles. She performed the voice of Faline in the 1942 Disney animated film Bambi.
